            I apologise for my late arrival; I have just come from a Select Committee.</p><p>
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_106wh' title='Col. 106WH &mdash; HC Deb 21 November 2001 vol 375 c106WH' name='column_106wh' href='#column_106wh' rel='bookmark'>106WH</a>
